name: Daisy Ridley - Embedding
description:
trained on 24 images of actress Daisy Ridley, 6000 steps. Most of my embeddings work better in illustrative models; this one seems to work better in SD1.5. Feel free to experiment. some models I've tested in do better with (emb-daisy:1.1), some with 0.9 I know there is already another TI of this person. I'm not trying to step on any toes, just releasing this by request. I hope you enjoy it! Let me know if you get any good pictures!

Samples in RinaMix2, SD 1.5, maybe a couple of others. Check PNG info button in the bottom right corner of the images.

modelVersions.name: v1
modelVersions.description: First TI version, remade from the training data used to make the older lessangrydaisy hypernet.
